OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FThe police watchdog has launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation of Merseyside Police
OL,9,Ffollowing a complaint from the man who
OL,10,Fserved 38 years behind bars for a
OL,11,Fmurder he didn't commit.
OL,13,FPeter Sullivan, 68, was jailed in 1987
OL,14,Ffor the murder of 21-year-old Diane
OL,15,FSindall, a florist and barmaid who was
OL,16,Fattacked violently while walking to a
OL,17,Fpetrol station in Birkenhead, in
OL,18,FWirral after her van broke down.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
