PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774642276
OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct says it had a referral from
OL,9,FMerseyside Police in January following
OL,10,Fa complaint from Peter Sullivan whose
OL,11,Fconviction was quashed at the Court of
OL,12,FAppeal in May 2025, because DNA
OL,13,Fevidence emerged which proved another,
OL,14,Funknown man was the killer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774642276
OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FIn a statement the IOPC said "We are
OL,8,Fspeaking to several agencies involved
OL,9,Fto determine what records are
OL,10,Favailable in relation to his case that
OL,11,Fmay be relevant to our inquiries. We
OL,12,Fcontinue to gather and carefully
OL,13,Freview this material, and have spoken
OL,14,Fto Mr Sullivan about his complaint, to
OL,15,Fdetermine the terms of reference for
OL,16,Four investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774642276
OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FIOPC Director Amanda Rowe said: "Mr
OL,8,FSullivan was a victim of one of the
OL,9,Fworst miscarriages of justice this
OL,10,Fcountry has ever seen. Our thoughts
OL,11,Fare with him as he continues to
OL,12,Frebuild his life.
OL,14,F"In light of the significant impact
OL,15,Fthis has had, as well as the severity
OL,16,Fof some of the allegations contained
OL,17,Fin the complaint, it is important for
OL,18,Fthese matters to be independently
OL,19,Finvestigated.
OL,26,@oD@aOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774642276
OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"The fact this took place almost 40
OL,8,Fyears ago poses substantial evidential
OL,9,Fchallenges, however we will do all we
OL,10,Fcan to progress our inquiries as
OL,11,Fquickly as we can, while taking all
OL,12,Fappropriate steps to ensure this does
OL,13,Fnot hinder the ongoing investigation
OL,14,Fby Merseyside Police into the horrific
OL,15,Fcrime against Ms Sindall."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
