OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FThe watchdog's investigation is is
OL,8,Fseparate to the Merseyside force's
OL,9,Fongoing criminal investigation into
OL,10,Fevents in 1986. That includes DNA
OL,11,Ftesting hundreds of men who were
OL,12,Fidentified in the original inquiry,
OL,13,Fthose samples have come from the area
OL,14,Fwhere Diane died and from all over the
OL,15,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
