PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774642276
OL,3,CPolice watchdog investigates force
OL,4,Cfollowing 'Beast of Birkenhead'
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FPeter Sullivan has raised a number of
OL,8,Fconcerns about how the force handled
OL,9,Fthe investigation in 1986 and his
OL,10,Farrest. It's now known he was not
OL,11,Fintitially given any legal
OL,12,Frepresentation and he claims he was
OL,13,Fphysically assaulted by officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
